rComments: Terry has an amazing sense of humour. The material can be a little dry. Overall, great professor. Easy to talk to. Comfortable class-environment.

The class is just based on the mid-term and final test, although the mid-term is somewhat easy, on the final he asked about almost every single thing, even though he says the final would be weighted more on the second half of the course, the test is full of questions from every single chapter in the book. He is not fair grading you in the final.
teacherRatingTags: ['Graded by few things', 'Lecture heavy', 'Get ready to read']
